27 Jan 2011 14:06






I like this one. That being said, a few issues:

In the first and third paragraphs, you state that there in a human effigy atop it. I would get rid of the mention in the first paragraph; it's just redundant.

I feel like this one is cut off early:

Scary Robot, cool
Human effigy, cooler
Crazy shit happens when it isn't well maintained, awesome
Potentially lethal scream, slightly cliche but still cool
Crazy shit includes….machines turning on. Neat, now what do they do?
Run.
So?
…that's it.


See what I mean? You have a cool foundation but you don't quite build on it. At first I thought this was actually a giant automaton, and was expecting it to run around all giant or something, which would have admittedly been pretty cool (if a bit too Gundam-esque). Point is, you need to up the creep in some way. Withholding vote for now.







